<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/52252742/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u52252742-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/52252742/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">石头</span>
